Author: terrifictulips
Text: I hope your coworker wasn't feeling clever for bringing up this scenario lol.  "Would you eat an uncooked, rotting dead baby that you probably held in your arms/interacted with for 5 days? ~The moral dilemma~"

Author: NyanDerp
Text: One of my coworkers brought up a philosophical question the other day, which went something like:  You're trapped in a cave with a baby. After 5 days of no rescue and no food, do you eat the (somehow still living) baby to stay alive?  Implying that humans can't live up to a month without food.
